we have creted eks cluster minimum with 3node.

All the required r=files, secrutiy,networking and IAM roles are in main.tf file and ekscluster.tf file.


command to run:

terraforn init

 this will initialise the task in backend


 terraform plan
   this will plan all the required task that are going to create, by runnig this command we can get to know if any errors in .tf files

terraform apply --auto-approve

  this command will create entire architecture , this will take some time to create all the resources.


If we want to destroy,

 terraform destroy --auto-approve, this will destroy entire resouce without any manual interaction.